#. Description of the plugin
#: stream-timer-for-wordpress.php
msgid "Schedule-based Twitch or YouTube stream embed. Plan multiple time windows in advance. Configurable in the backend, insert via shortcode [stream_timer]. Performance optimized: assets load only when the shortcode is present and a window is active."
msgstr ""

